    Scope and Contents
Council on Community Relations file includes meeting minutes and memoranda.  The committees of the two  councils were: Continuing Education, Social Relations, Social Planning, Building Committee (Interim) and Building Committee (Permanent). Meeting mnutes contain information regarding faculty laod, construction projects, student teacher ratio and university assembly council membership.  Reports include draft of Council Committee structure and various membership rosters.  Memoranda are from committee members to University assembly members and the SSU University Community.  
  
